{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "倒帶獨白", "storyInfo": "盧西恩道出莫伊拉為姐姐勞拉復仇的每一步，莫伊拉也在他的步步緊逼之下發現她並不存在於勞拉的人生之中。而此時莫伊拉安裝的破壞裝置生效，地塊撞向天災，劇組人員的性命危在旦夕，一切都無法回頭了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_rglk1phantomcastle_intro", "key": "$m_sys_rglk1phantomcastle_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你在格蕾塔女士解散劇組之後給出的各種選擇裡，選擇了當偵探，盧西恩先生。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用虛張聲勢。我知道，你並不害怕我點破它。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果能讓更多人知道勞拉墜亡的真相以及劇組成員的所作所為，你甚至會在適當的時機主動暴露自己。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但不是現在。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都結束了，莫伊拉。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直隱藏得很好，單純的身分和無辜的外表是很理想的掩護。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾乎每次兇案發生時，你都與蒂比在一起，那位布景噴畫師很信任你，她為你提供了不在場證明……哪怕你曾中途離開。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在想來，劇組發生的每起“意外”，都或多或少與你有關。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓死於被替換的道具刀，原先的道具組長被辭退，你順理成章接手他的工作，獲得了更多作案的機會。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二起“意外”……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——謝莉走入冷凍庫。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，在那之前她已起了殺心，只是未能成功。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士，還記得嗎？謝莉小姐曾因陷入幻覺拖延了拍攝。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當她僵在原地無法動彈的時候，沉重的貨箱從天而降……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你救下了謝莉，莫伊拉僅憑一人之力拉住了貨箱的繩索，避免你們受傷……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那並不是好心的順手之勞。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時所有人都被謝莉小姐的行動吸引，極少有人會注意到空中懸吊的貨箱……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更別說她在第一時間就出現在繩索的另一端。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有在繩索上做手腳的人，才能做出如此迅速的反應……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也正是這次殺人未遂讓“謝莉小姐會被幻覺影響”成為劇組人人皆知的事實，於是你順水推舟……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道她最深的惡夢。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把我誤認成勞拉姐姐，對我吐露了罪惡的秘密……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但直到最後，她都沒向姐姐懺悔，反倒開始責怪姐姐的逾矩……她該死。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於瑪麗昂和邁克爾……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾只把我當成一個任人指使的無辜女生，他猜不到我才是要向他索命的兇手，連偷偷逃離地塊這樣攸關性命的大事也委託我幫忙。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而瑪麗昂甚至認為自己絲毫不需要為當年的事情負責，她更該死！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃？一個都逃不掉！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們知道嗎？姐姐承受了那麼多痛苦與惡意，但她隻字不提，只說自己在劇組裡收穫了多少經驗與快樂……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我憂心自己無法勝任道具師工作時，當我在劇組受到排擠偷偷掉眼淚時……她都會用自己的例子來安慰我、鼓勵我……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#16$2"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但直到她過世之後，我才知道，你們提供給她的到底是什麼待遇！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#16$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔，而你現在看著我的眼神裡竟然充滿了……疑惑？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#17$2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道忘了自己是怎樣收買警方和媒體，壓下姐姐的死，把意外變成電影中亦真亦假的戲，讓她死後都不得安寧嗎！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#17$2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，莫伊拉。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士並未遺忘自己的所作所為，她只是在懷疑你的真實身分。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身分？劇組的道具師，不起眼的札拉克，犯下累累罪行的復仇者……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉，並沒有妹妹。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她從不存在於你的人生。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在……說什麼？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這又是哪種逼問的手段？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#15$2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五年前的事故之後，我曾向勞拉的家人發了一筆撫恤金。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了保證勞拉的家庭成員甚至是遠親都不會向外透露她已死的真相，我僱人仔細調查了她的家庭情況。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩告訴我他推理出的真相後，我一度難以置信，所以再次比對了勞拉的家庭成員名單……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾……裡面並沒有“莫伊拉”。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#16$2"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你說謊！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#16$2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於你身上發生的一切，我知道該如何解釋。但你需要花時間接受它。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下那把匕首，莫伊拉。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它本不該屬於你。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下……？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經來不及了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"durat